      "author": "lc0rp",
      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n\r\n### Most Notable\r\n\r\n**Mobile compatibility: sync on the go!**\r\n\r\nKeepSidian now runs on **Android and iOS**, so you can sync on the go 🚀  \r\nThis unlocks some pretty delightful workflows. One community member captures ideas with **Google Keep** on their smartwatch and has them syncing into **Obsidian** in near real time. Drop a note if you end up using this feature. We'd love to continue refining it based on you feedback.\r\n\r\n### New Features\r\n\r\n- Mobile-friendly token retrieval and settings UI\r\n- Desktop token retrieval wizard overhaul, now offering two browser automation options to ease the  \r\n\r\n### UX and Reliability\r\n\r\n- Sync notices are faster and now contain a progress indicator.\r\n- General improvement in two-way sync reliability.\r\n- Safer handling of missing attachment URLs.\r\n\r\n## Full Changelog\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/lc0rp/KeepSidian/compare/1.1.3...2.0.3\r\n\r\nKeep syncing!",
